{"tid":2126540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國駐成都總領館已降下國旗　部分中國員工將被解僱","createTime":"2020-07-27T01:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T03:30:31.000Z","uid":23707,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f71077fad779f8f6865f8cfc27d62b8f8193e3f5","tid":2126540,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:52:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200727/bkn-20200727000008481-0727_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200727%2Fbkn-20200727000008481-0727_00972_001.html&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=13685e60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200727/bkn-20200727000008481-0727_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國早前要求關閉中國駐德州休斯敦總領事館，中國外交部上周五（24日）要求美國駐成都總領事館72小時內關閉。根據對等原則，該館於香港時間周一（27日）上午10時前關閉。央視旗下的環球電視網（CGTN）周日（26日）報道，該館內部分中國員工將被解僱，他們正與總領事館交涉解聘方案。周日晚上，美國駐成都總領館開始拆除門口徽標。周一清晨6時許，館內的美國國旗已降下。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述一名駐成都總領事館不願透露姓名的員工透露，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">一些中國員工將被解僱。</span></span>該員工又指，一些美國員工不會太快離開中國，因為他們還有很多工作要做，處理完才會離開。但他未提及具體的工作內容。<br />\n<br />\n過去一日，美國駐成都總領事館大門口的美國國徽及門口銘牌已拆下，但入口處仍掛有美國國旗，車輛及人員從周日凌晨起頻繁進出，更有5輛重型卡車在晚上10時許進入總領事館，有大木箱被吊裝在重型卡車上。<br />\n<br />\n駐成都總領事林杰偉的夫人莊祖宜本月1日在微博發文稱，今年2月1日丈夫告知她所有外交人員家屬都必須撤離中國，「試想二戰前猶太人為了躲納粹而離開家是否就像這樣」。其中「猶太人躲納粹」的類比，引來內地網民批評：「陰陽怪氣。」據悉，莊祖宜生於台灣，是哥倫比亞大學人類學碩士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95e80b8064664bf713c295ede49723ba560c43f","tid":2126540,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"加速成咁，班支仔仲係到打飛機，就知，文明世界有運行了"},{"pid":"badbc1b988fa53df9ff4d51a259bcb83c1f56d8f","tid":2126540,"uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d95e80b8064664bf713c295ede49723ba560c43f","tid":2126540,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"加速成咁，班支仔仲係到打飛機，就知，文明世界有運行了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"失業都可以打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f98d0e0e98234705087f9839c5984a7155beee","tid":2126540,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fd2d92ecd208b4805a316db2096bfa788c298e","tid":2126540,"uid":252142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ea3b5438c20f698d68e463c4999f2b23412bec7","tid":2126540,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d95e80b8064664bf713c295ede49723ba560c43f","tid":2126540,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"加速成咁，班支仔仲係到打飛機，就知，文明世界有運行了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:23:53.000Z","msg":"咩呀  西方社會關注西藏  關左成都  對美國好大影響架 （好似係） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1636cc059ef2cbedc14233d95b0f3907708f628","tid":2126540,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:25:04.000Z","msg":"有無綠卡"},{"pid":"8775fe66eade0b8b67b153a7b73237d06f81c5a9","tid":2126540,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:26:38.000Z","msg":"外匯收入又跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3447a6186acd74ca87150eedfd9a87e5938e52d","tid":2126540,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7fd2d92ecd208b4805a316db2096bfa788c298e","tid":2126540,"uid":252142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:27:17.000Z